answers.body_markdown:
Your `graphql` HOC is imported from `react-apollo`, but the `ApolloProvider` you are using is imported from `@apollo/react-hooks`. Because these are different packages, the context your provider is creating is not the same as what the HOC is looking for. Even if you&#39;re using hooks, there&#39;s no need for the `@apollo/react-hooks` dependency at all. Just:

```
import { ApolloProvider } from &#39;react-apollo&#39;
import { graphql, useQuery, Query /* etc. */ } from &#39;react-apollo&#39;
```

